{"tid":2388883,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【直擊單位】屯門龍珠島放盤 300萬唔駛就可上車？","createTime":"2021-01-31T12:41:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T05:10:27.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"028cf9516a9afde4786602b4d40a7edabb205123","tid":2388883,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:41:52.000Z","msg":"【直擊單位】屯門龍珠島放盤 300萬唔駛就可上車？<br />\n20:09 2021/01/31<br />\n<br />\n&quot;龍珠島放盤一向備市場關注！龍珠島位處屯門東南面，是一個鄰近黃金海岸的離島。龍珠島上設有長堤，供住戶步行及駕車出入龍珠島與青山公路。龍珠島亦設有村巴前往至黃金海岸商場、三聖村等地。雖然龍珠島交通或會較爲不便，但當聽到不用300萬就可以上車，你又會不會對龍珠島有興趣......<br />\n<br />\n單位為7座4室，實用面積286平方呎的開放式戶......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2860173/%E3%80%90%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%91%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%BE%8D%E7%8F%A0%E5%B3%B6%E6%94%BE%E7%9B%A4%20300%E8%90%AC%E5%94%94%E9%A7%9B%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%EF%BC%9F?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2860173%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E9%25BE%258D%25E7%258F%25A0%25E5%25B3%25B6%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%259B%25A4%2520300%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%25A7%259B%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25EF%25BC%259F%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=fdc2e37c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2860173/%E3%80%90%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E3%80%91%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E9%BE%8D%E7%8F%A0%E5%B3%B6%E6%94%BE%E7%9B%A4%20300%E8%90%AC%E5%94%94%E9%A7%9B%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%EF%BC%9F?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">單位叫價只是288萬，簡直是上車人士「恩物」! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f56cd81cbcc78273400621d352b14a5c42ab6129","tid":2388883,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-3